Changes since version 1.7
- list_tables() works properly now.

Changes since version 1.6

- Module works with sqlite3 now, instead of dumping core.
- Reworked configure tests to be more robust.
- Include binary encoding and decoding methods that are not part
  of the sqlite core.

Changes since version 1.5

- Better error messages from failed queries.

Changes since version 1.4

- Fix a bug that can cause segfaults when results contain nulls.

- Fix a number of compilation bugs

